item.title: Sorry. Maybe wrong section. Forgive me! ;p
item.dc:creator: @The_Reaper_X The Reaper X
item.description:
@The_Reaper_X wrote:

Okay, i can’t walk away from this without informing everyone.

winterLove is a guy first of all, and he wasn’t the “only one” to create “the first source”. He was just one of the only one’s to release the beginning of rs emulation.

You’re completely ignorant if you’re claiming to be able to criticize winterLove’s work. RS emulation was for EMULATION not reproduction. People have said before winterLove would be disappointed if he saw what we’ve created with his work. I really don’t even know half of the story on how all of this came about, but I kno he didn’t plan on people mass releasing reproductions of his source on RSPS forums such as mscp.

X Screech X:

Creator of a weak base,

If you knew any better, you wouldn’t be far without winterLove’s work.
